Definition: usually at the beginning of a sentence) apparently modifying a word other than the word intended: e.g., `flying across the country' in `flying across the country the Rockies came into view'
Synonyms: dangling_modifier, a, participle, usually, at, the, beginning, of, sentence, apparently, modifying, word, other, than, intended, e, g, flying, across, country, in, Rockies, came, into, view
Category: noun.communication
